Justin Whalin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justin_Whalin 0 Justin Garrett Whalin (born September 6, 1974) is an American actor. He is known for his roles as the teenage Andy Barclay in Child's Play 3 and Jimmy Olsen in the American television series Lois Clark: The New Adventures of Superman.
